OL,3,CEquality Commission to seek clarity
OL,4,Cfrom High Court on gender ruling
OL,6,FGuidance will be sought from the High
OL,7,FCourt in Belfast over the effect a
OL,8,Flandmark Supreme Court ruling on
OL,9,Fgender will have in Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FThe Equality Commission in Northern
OL,12,FIreland has said that there is
OL,13,F"significant" legal uncertainty in the
OL,14,Fwake of the ruling, including how it
OL,15,Finteracts with existing equality law
OL,16,Fand with Article 2 of the Windsor
OL,17,FFramework.
