OL,3,CEquality Commission to seek clarity
OL,4,Cfrom High Court on gender ruling
OL,6,FChief Commissioner of the Equality
OL,7,FCommission Geraldine McGahey said they
OL,8,Fwould consult with other parties on
OL,9,Fwhether they wish to join the legal
OL,10,Fproceedings on the "nuanced and
OL,11,Fcomplicated" issue.
OL,13,FMs McGahey said through referring the
OL,14,Fissue to the courts, they hoped to
OL,15,Favoid "the toxicity which has
OL,16,Fsometimes characterised the debate".
