OL,3,CEquality Commission to seek clarity
OL,4,Cfrom High Court on gender ruling
OL,6,FThe Supreme Court in London declared
OL,7,Fin April that the terms "woman" and
OL,8,F"sex" in the 2010 Equality Act "refer
OL,9,Fto a biological woman and biological
OL,10,Fsex".
OL,12,FThe ruling has been interpreted to
OL,13,Fmean that transgender women can be
OL,14,Fexcluded from women-only spaces such
OL,15,Fas toilets and changing rooms.
OL,17,FHowever, the Equality Act 2010 does
OL,18,Fnot cover Northern Ireland.
