OL,3,CEquality Commission to seek clarity
OL,4,Cfrom High Court on gender ruling
OL,6,FThe Equality Commission was to prepare
OL,7,Fguidance on the ruling's potential
OL,8,Fimplications on Stormont departments.
OL,10,FIn a legal paper published by the
OL,11,FEquality Commission on Friday, it said
OL,12,Fit would request legal clarity from
OL,13,Fthe High Court.
OL,15,FThe Commission said that once the High
OL,16,FCourt decides on the matter, and
OL,17,Fsubject to any appeals, the Commission
OL,18,Fwill then produce its draft guidance,
OL,19,Fwhich will be subject to further
OL,20,Fconsultation.
