OL,3,CEquality Commission to seek clarity
OL,4,Cfrom High Court on gender ruling
OL,6,FMs McGahey said: "After much
OL,7,Fconsideration and analysis, the
OL,8,FCommission has concluded that the
OL,9,Fsituation in Northern Ireland, in
OL,10,Frespect of this matter, is much more
OL,11,Fnuanced and complicated, and there is
OL,12,Fsignificant uncertainty due to our
OL,13,Funique legal landscape.
OL,15,F"We have no interest in merely
OL,16,Fspeculating as to how a court might
OL,17,Fdetermine these issues in the future.
OL,18,FWe will not answer these legal
OL,19,Funcertainties by weighing the
OL,20,Farguments 'for' and 'against'.
OL,26,@nD@ROUwD@AOU
