OL,3,CEquality Commission to seek clarity
OL,4,Cfrom High Court on gender ruling
OL,6,F"It is important that the Commission
OL,7,Fshows leadership as people and their
OL,8,Flives are at the heart of this issue.
OL,10,F"To achieve greater long-term
OL,11,Fcertainty and clarity for all
OL,12,Finvolved, the Commission will be
OL,13,Fseeking a declaration from the courts
OL,14,Fto address several questions regarding
OL,15,Fthe significant legal uncertainties.
OL,17,F"Our equality laws do not sit in
OL,18,Fisolation; they interact with other
OL,19,Flaws and regulations for which the
OL,20,FCommission does not have a remit.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
