OL,6,F"We believe other bodies and
OL,7,Forganisations will also require
OL,8,Fclarification on the legal position in
OL,9,Frelation to their own areas of work
OL,10,Fand may join the Commission in its
OL,11,Flegal proceedings.
OL,13,F"The Commission will issue Pre-Action
OL,14,FProtocol letters to government
OL,15,Fdepartments and other public bodies
OL,16,Fwith legal responsibilities
OL,17,Fpotentially affected by the judgment
OL,18,Fand to other interested parties.
