OL,6,F"The Commission will also commence a
OL,7,Fwider consultation process for all
OL,8,Finterested stakeholders."
OL,10,FShe said the Commission wants to give
OL,11,Feveryone the opportunity to engage and
OL,12,Fwill welcome input from all
OL,13,Fstakeholders.
OL,15,F"We fully recognise the challenges
OL,16,Ffaced by employers and service
OL,17,Fproviders as they try to navigate
OL,18,Fthese uncertainties," she said.
