OL,6,F"We aim to create a robust framework
OL,7,Ffor offering guidance, rather than
OL,8,Fbeing subject to numerous legal
OL,9,Funcertainties that may be contested in
OL,10,Fthe courts over the coming years at
OL,11,Fpotentially great cost to the public
OL,12,Fpurse.
OL,14,F"By adopting this approach, we hope to
OL,15,Favoid the toxicity which has sometimes
OL,16,Fcharacterised the debate around how to
OL,17,Fbalance the rights of biological women
OL,18,Fand transgender women by creating a
OL,19,Fspace for debate and adjudication by
OL,20,Fthe courts.
