OL,6,FThe Upper Bann representative said
OL,7,Forganisations should "not be
OL,8,Fdistracted or deterred" by the
OL,9,Fcommission's response and public
OL,10,Fauthorities should "move decisively to
OL,11,Fimplement" the Supreme Court ruling.
OL,13,F"The recent judgment by the Supreme
OL,14,FCourt was a common-sense ruling that
OL,15,Freaffirmed the importance of sex-based
OL,16,Fprotections," she said.
OL,18,F"This was a victory for the rights of
OL,19,Fwomen and girls, providing clarity and
OL,20,Freassurance, in particular, around the
OL,21,Fprovision of single-sex spaces.
